Package com.foley.graph.core

Class AbstractGraph<V,​E>

java.lang.Object
com.foley.graph.core.AbstractGraph<V,​E>
Type Parameters:
V - The type of vertices in the graph
E - The type of cost between vertices in the graph
All Implemented Interfaces:
Graph<V,​E>
Direct Known Subclasses:
BasicGraph, BasicHashGraph
public abstract class AbstractGraph<V,​E> extends Object implements Graph<V,​E>
This class provides a skeletal impmlementation of the Graph interface. It provides a backing Set for storing the vertices belonging to the graph
